		    <h2>Key Features</h2>

<h3>1. Story-driven Gameplay:</h3>
<p>The story revolves around the Mysterious virus which has spread all over the world and turns people into violent creatures. Now the role of the protagonist is to find the answer to all this chaos in this dangerous world.</p>

