<h3>3. Combat System:</h3>
<p>This combat system is mainly focused over the melee and player skill and strategy. Player will be going to face both human enemies and supernatural enemies. There are requirements to tackle different enemies.</p>

<h3>4. Emotional Narrative:</h3>
